column5: I just got my new boat last night. I was looking things over today and see condensation inside the screen on the fish finder. It was cold and wet all day today. Is this normal, or a bad thing. I think I should take it right back. Opinions?
Take it right back.  I only time i had that happen the fishfinder was toast shortly after.
Same here, toast. The dealer swapped it out in a heartbeat. Jim
Take it back for sure........Moisture and electronics don't mix,,,,,,,Moisture always wins..
